title: Hawaiian Local Reacts To Like A Dragon: Infinite Wealth
description:
From Waikiki Beach and shave ice to the Ala Wai Canal and the International Marketplace, Richard Li compares Like A Dragon: Infinite Wealth's portrayal of Hawaii to his own knowledge of the islands after growing up in Honolulu.

title: Firearms Expert Reacts To PALWORLD's Guns
description:
